{"tid":2384120,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉財報好壞參半，但「能源業務」起飛","createTime":"2021-01-28T10:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T13:52:15.000Z","uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60493ce173513c0e402dd175cecd4677bbd25b91","tid":2384120,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"特斯拉 27 日公布加入 S&amp;P 500 以來第一份財報，雖第四季獲利不如預期、好壞參半，<strong><span class=\"red\">但值得注意的是，馬斯克（Elon Musk）壓在能源儲存和太陽能領域的賭注，開始獲得回報了。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據特斯拉公布的第四季財報，<strong><span class=\"red\">能源業務（storage business）可說是該公司表現最亮眼的 MVP，季度同比增長接近 200％。</span></strong>根據特斯拉的說法，其電池部署總量在一年內首次超過 3 Gwh，與 2019 年相比增長 83％；另一方面，<strong><span class=\"red\">太陽能業務也照到了充足的陽光，表現也值得關注，2020 年，特斯拉太陽能安裝量增加到 205 MW，比上一年增加了 18％</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">第四季特斯拉能源業務收入達 7.52 億美元，相比去年同期的 4.36 億美元成長不少。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>特斯拉可能是拜登「綠色新政」的最大受益者？</strong><br />\n<br />\n特斯拉雖以「電動車」廣為人知，但該公司在 2016 年收購 SolarCity 後，開啟了屋頂太陽能系統的製造與安裝相關業務&mdash;&mdash;SolarCity 曾是美國最大太陽能板安裝業者&mdash;&mdash;開始積極布局能源版圖，現在該公司不但擁有永不斷電的太陽能 家用蓄電系統 Powerwall，近日更推出新款的 「太陽能變流器」，讓變流器製造商類股暴跌，可見其在太陽能市場的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">《TechCrunch》指出，這可能只是特斯拉能源業務即將掀起波瀾的開始，因為該公司可望從新任總統拜登（Joe Biden）的綠能政策中獲益。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n拜登在上任後隨即提出 2 兆美元的「綠色新政」（Green New Deal），包括促進電動車普及化、廣泛設置汽車充電站、電網更新等，並預計在全美部署公用事業規模級電池儲能設備，這些政策都會需要大量的太陽能裝置，並且需要大型電池來儲存可再生能源。"},{"pid":"6a22793ecaa4a4b32a4b598166ddad96f821de70","tid":2384120,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:00:39.000Z","msg":"Tesla能源業務數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq8PgBn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq8PgBn.jpg&h=feae395a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgRpPWn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgRpPWn.jpg&h=1605225f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f81e53f67c5a1413b029b4591f83698ed99778f","tid":2384120,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2021/01/28/tesla-storage-business/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2021%2F01%2F28%2Ftesla-storage-business%2F&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=c90a1adc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2021/01/28/tesla-storage-business/</a>"},{"pid":"a34666673c0442827185388555ba00ca23fe3499","tid":2384120,"uid":18085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"tsla跌就加貨 長線睇7000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11f5bf69b5d5664fe498ebf2a0c66d281522ccf","tid":2384120,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a34666673c0442827185388555ba00ca23fe3499","tid":2384120,"uid":18085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"tsla跌就加貨 長線睇7000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"已加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ff49c767b8f42be13a624d1a67635f81a2828e","tid":2384120,"uid":18085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e11f5bf69b5d5664fe498ebf2a0c66d281522ccf","tid":2384120,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a34666673c0442827185388555ba00ca23fe3499","tid":2384120,"uid":18085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"tsla跌就加貨 長線睇7000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"已加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c